long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The extension for GreenBee employees to auto fill values on ComEd's Nexant website using data from Zoho's creator form. This extension can fill out customer information, facility information, room information, and measure information on the Nexant page with data from Zoho. The extension will fetch deals from Zoho and once a deal is selected, it will then let you select which facility you want to auto complete the data for.
